name: Modern Assets Pack 01 - Commercial Use Allowed
name_original: Modern Assets Pack 01 - Commercial Use Allowed
description:
This pack contains modern assets or tokens for VTT maps and map softwares for you to have more options! These can be used in any commercial or personal project of yours. 

This pack contains:
- An accessibility ramp
- A microwave
- A church bell
- A sock
- A picnic table
- A tool box
- An industrial vacuum cleaner
- A first-aid kit
- A towel
- A syringe
- A small broom and dustpan

* Items are not to scale
